            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Neovim isn't freezing - `:make` is just run non-interactively, i.e. you can't send inputs to it. I would recommend using something like `:sp term://node inspect %` instead - the terminal is interactive. If you want to run that on each save, something like `:au BufWrite file.js sp term://node inspect %` would do that.\r\n\r\nI think this issue could be considered a duplicate of https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/1496 .",
